    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "In order to generate a gitlab CI dynamic pipeline, you need to make sure \"mirrors\" keyword is defined in `spack.yaml` itself. If the mirror is in an external config file, I get an error message.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```console\r\n-bash-4.2$ spack ci generate\r\n==> Warning: included configuration files should be updated manually [files=./, ../config.yaml, ../mirrors.yaml, ../modules.yaml, ../repos.yaml]\r\n==> Error: spack ci generate requires an env containing a mirror\r\n```",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
}